# Node.js dependencies and build artifacts

# Ignore node_modules in all folders
**/node_modules/

# Ignore build output directories commonly used
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.next/
**/.nuxt/
**/out/

# Ignore package-lock and yarn lock files
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml

# Ignore coverage reports
**/coverage/

# Ignore temporary files
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*